HEADWORD: arb
<hw>arb</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Shortened from
<ets>arbitrageur</ets>.]</ety> <def>Someone who engages in arbitrage
(who purchases securities in one market for immediate resale in another
in the hope of profiting from the price differential); shortened form of
<er>arbitrageur</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> arbitrageur</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

